title: RIP Kane Tanaka | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 73
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
The BABES are finally back together to celebrate the life of Kane Tanaka! Kane lived a glorious 119 years filled with love, lust, and laughter. Sal and Chris share a few stories from the times Kane visited Staten Island. Send us any stories you shared with Kane on our socials using #Kancelled. Elon Musk takes over twitter and the babes don't know what to think. Mike Tyson has a meltdown on a flight. Anyone else afraid of hackers? Man marries a hologram. Shout out NUKES and Madonna! THE BABES ARE BACK!!!
Rate us on iTunes!
